.top
  = render 'layouts/header'
  .top-contents
    .top-content__intoroduction
      %h2.top-intoroduction-subtitle FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
      %ul.top-intoroduction-lists
        %li.top-intoroduction-list
          .top-intoroduction-list__pict
            %span.top-intoroduction-list__number 1
            = image_tag "pict-reason-01.jpg", class: "banner__main-image"
          %h3.top-intoroduction-list__text
            %span.top-span 3分
            ですぐに出品
          %p.top-intoroduction-list__description
            スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
        %li.top-intoroduction-list
          .top-intoroduction-list__pict
            %span.top-intoroduction-list__number 2
            = image_tag "pict-reason-02.jpg", class: "banner__main-image"
          %h3.top-intoroduction-list__text
            %span シンプル
            で使いやすい
          %p.top-intoroduction-list__description
            めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
        %li.top-intoroduction-list-last
          .top-intoroduction-list__pict
            %span.top-intoroduction-list__number 3
            = image_tag "pict-reason-03.jpg", class: "banner__main-image"
          %h3.top-intoroduction-list__text
            手数料
            %span.top-span 業界最安
          %p.top-intoroduction-list__description
            最大3%でお得に出品&amp;購入！
    .top-content__futures
      %h2.top-futures-subtitle FURIMAの特徴
      .top-futuers-lists
        .top-futures-list
          .top-futures-list__pict
            = image_tag 'icon-01.png'
          %h3.top-futures-list__text
            簡単に売り買いできる
          %p.top-futures-list__description
            スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
        .top-futures-list
          .top-futures-list__pict
            = image_tag "icon-03.png"
          %h3.top-futures-list__text
            売上金は即日振込みに対応
          %p.top-futures-list__description
            午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
        .top-futures-list
          .top-futures-list__pict
            = image_tag "icon-04.png"
          %h3.top-futures-list__text
            様々な支払いに対応
          %p.top-futures-list__description
            お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
  = render 'layouts/banner'
  = render 'layouts/footer'
  = render 'layouts/purchase-btn'
